Of the 13 Commission members:
1 shall be the Secretary of Agriculture or the designee of the Secretary of Agriculture, as an ex officio nonvoting member;
1 shall be the Secretary of Natural Resources or the designee of the Secretary of Natural Resources, as an ex officio nonvoting member;
5 shall represent the seafood packers in this State, at least 3 of whom shall be members of the Chesapeake Bay Seafood Industries Association;
2 shall be licensed Maryland watermen;
1 shall represent the retail food industry in this State;
1 shall represent the aquaculture industry in this State; and
2 shall be consumer members.

The terms of the initial voting members of the Commission expire as follows:
2 in 1988;
3 in 1989;
3 in 1990; and
3 in 1991.
